column5: finally getting around to posting pics of the new boat i picked up this summer,,runs like a dream ,great on gas and the smooth ride is awsome,,had to put her away for the winter but looking forward to the spring.
those seats look more comfy than the ones in my Mazda truck
Very nice rig !!!Love the color and that nice black Merc hangin off the back Congrats !!

yup, that will do just fine!
Nice Ride and Looks Great!!  Rick
